    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The xdg_wm_base interface is exposed as a global object enabling clients to turn their wl_surfaces into windows in a desktop environment. It defines the basic functionality needed for clients and the compositor to create windows that can be dragged, resized, maximized, etc, as well as creating transient windows such as popup menus. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
